Installation Guide How To Install Perfectly？ Thank you for your choice and purchase! For best installation, please read the installation tutorial carefully before use. We are always go extra mile to provide with best products and services. NOTE: 1.There is no hole in the flash position. Don't install it upside down. 2.Repeated removal will affect adhesion. 3.When installing the camera lens protector, make sure that there is no dust around the lens, and press repeatedly until it sticks tightly.

What materials are screen protectors and camera lens protectors made of? Tempered glass or plastic? The screen protector is made of tempered glass, and the camera lens protector is made of tempered glass and polymethyl methacrylate. Tempered or tempered glass is a safety increases glass strength and flexibility by controlling heat or chemistry. Why is the tempered glass little smaller than the actual screen of the mobile phone? In order to suitable for most phone cases on the market, and minimize bubbles, cracking and came off, so QHOHQ screen protector little smaller on the sides. How can I remove air bubbles? Use the kit in the package to clean the screen before placing the screen protector. If there are bubbles, please take a thin cloth and press the bubbles gently with your fingers, The thin cloth is to prevent scratching the protector. Is this product good to use? Yes, it touch sensitive, shatterproof, bubbleproof, scratch resistant；Suitable for most phone case on the market. Come with gadgets to make it easy for you to operate; Certified by ROHS Environmental and SGS Drop Test Certification. So own it now! How do I connect the seller for a replacement or return? reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Three for the price of one!
reviews.reviewText: These protectors come three to a pack so overall the pricing is great. Screen protector went on without a hitch. I did pit the camera lense protector on and second day after installing my phone slipped off my lap and the lense protector cracked! What a time I had removing that cracked protector, the adhesive was on there to stay! I elected not to put a new lense protector back on even though there were extras. The screen protector is great and I know it does its job to protect my screen. I wouldn’t hesitate to recommend the screen protector.

reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Easy to apply
reviews.reviewText: Worked right the first time! I've had screen protectors that would not apply easily -- bubbled, had to remove and retry. Easy instructions and it's a three pack! Highly recommend.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars This product is amazing!!!
reviews.reviewText: I had never bought a screen protector before, but with my latest iphone, I decided to. Due to my clumsiness, I have dropped it once, cracking the screen protector, and then again cracking the camera lens protector. This latest time, the iphone fell out of my pocket, not realizing it. Thought I had lost the phone. In any case, I did recover it. It looks like it had been run over as both the screen protector and case were damaged. Got home popped the old screen protector off (I do find it is easier to use a pocket knife to remove it, than trying to use the tool they provide. Just have to be a bit careful), installed a new shield and the phone is good as new (still seems to work even having been run over!)(a testament to Apple?). Anyway, this product is well worth the purchase. I have bought another pack of them. Given my history, I will use them!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on January 27, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars A must buy if you drop your phone a lot
reviews.reviewText: Highly recommend. I love this kit so much. I’ve bought it twice over the course of a year and a half. The screen protectors for the touch screen and the cameras are so worth it. The pry bar that comes with this kit makes replacing both protectors so easy. The guide for the front screen ensures that you have a perfect placement every time. The directions in the case come with pictures and it’s really easy to follow the steps. Comes with 3 replacement screens for both the camera and the front screen. They hold up well. I’ve never had a scratch on my actual device thanks to these bad boys. Saved my rear camera from damage while we were traveling. Doesn’t leave a weird residue on your device when you replace them. Compatible with iPhone 14.
